data.title: WTF Definition & Meaning
data.meta_description: WTF definition: what the fuck (a euphemistic initialism used to express anger, impatience, surprise, etc., without explicit vulgarity). . See examples of WTF used in a sentence.
data.text:
Discover More

Example Sentences

The Golden Globes TV nominations reliably elicit a WTF reaction.

And on the other are the folk, numbers unknown, who would pretty much say to Alexander, WTF are you talking about?

And Ben Affleck is the WTF-casting-turned-brilliant performance leading them all.

This conscious uncoupling was a big deal because WTF is that even.
